{"tid":655432,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你地有無分散銀同散紙？","createTime":"2018-05-06T13:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T13:42:20.000Z","uid":42752,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8990fdc94764b7c4649db3a94a9d7c330561761","tid":655432,"uid":42752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"剛才我去買野食，見到有張五十蚊係銀包<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：唔該，我想唱散紙（微笑）<br />\n收銀：好啊無問題（微笑）<br />\n<br />\n之後俾左五個十蚊硬幣我，我呆左<br />\n我：唔該，我要散紙(微笑)<br />\n收銀:咪俾左咯(眼超超）<br />\n我：得！我要翻五十蚊<br />\n收銀：妖！<br />\n<br />\n咁你地有無分開叫散銀同散紙？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然有分 唔係銀同紙把撚啊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啊屌 樓主咪撚成個女人咁啦"},{"pid":"13550772f713a415757ef3ef41ef3bf57906d6e0","tid":655432,"uid":1123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"會講清楚做5張十蚊紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ca76a0b7defd080d51dbfefdb831cd5ad2e724","tid":655432,"uid":81252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"你要唱幾多就同人講要咩<br />\n例如五個十蚊銀or五張十蚊紙"},{"pid":"cd0bf8a0555ca695ae3fec4e53c087a1c8d95d40","tid":655432,"uid":27458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"我當人地聽唔明<br />\n你唔識換個方法講？"},{"pid":"b7d9178eef06790999ad3795f583413e3f9f3e19","tid":655432,"uid":37005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:35:41.000Z","msg":"先唔講有冇分 但你都好怪姐要唱但又唔講點唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人哋搞錯咗又唔識講清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a76bf3d9f619947aa7e90065fd40af3c5a1363","tid":655432,"uid":42752,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cd0bf8a0555ca695ae3